      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="how-a-roadmap-differs-from-an-seo-strategy"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>A strategy states what you want to achieve. A roadmap states what happens next week. The strategy says "rank for plumber keywords in Denver." The roadmap says "publish emergency-plumber-denver on April 22, assigned to Maria, targeting 480 monthly searches."</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
